{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给黄炎培的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给黄炎培的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月15日）任老："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮税事，我告陈薄后，已有复信，兹付上请阅。如有意见，请再告。原件尊处可抄存，然后还我。此祝健康！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月十五日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]黄炎培，字任之，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]陈，指陈云，当时任政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。薄，指薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":396,"page_end":396},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}